Police have launched an investigation after two people were found dead in a house in Suffolk. 
Officers were called to the property on Stowupland Street, Stowmarket, at 1.45pm yesterday afternoon and found a man and a woman dead inside. 
Their deaths are currently being treated as unexplained.
